    <description>In Wall Relay Switch&lt;br /&gt&lt;h1&gtOverview&lt;/h1&gt&lt;p&gtVision ZL7431US In-wall 1 relay switch&lt;/p&gt &lt;br /&gt&lt;h2&gtInclusion Information&lt;/h2&gt&lt;ul&gt&lt;li&gtTurn on and turn off the wall switch that connects with ZL 7431 module 4 times to be included&lt;/li&gt &lt;li&gt(or press the Program SW 4 times within 2 seconds to be included),&lt;/li&gt &lt;/ul&gt&lt;p&gtthen LED shall stop flashing.Â &lt;/p&gt &lt;br /&gt&lt;h2&gtExclusion Information&lt;/h2&gt&lt;ul&gt&lt;li&gtTurn on and turn off the wall switch that connects with ZL 7431 module 4 times to be excluded&lt;/li&gt &lt;li&gt(or press the Program SW 4 times within 2 seconds to be excluded),&lt;/li&gt &lt;/ul&gt&lt;p&gtthen LED shall start flashing&lt;/p&gt</description>
